name: Void Engine
description:
Submission  for the Mini Jam 67. Theme: Void Limitation: No enemies.

You are alone with unstable Void Engine trapped in space station. To survive use all items that you can handle and throw it into the void. Don't let the engine stop and don't overload it. Keep the balance and survive longer.

All decks, alert! Void Engine is damaged. I repeat, Void Engine is damaged. Sending instructions...

Hope it helps! Good luck and have fun...
